Place this in /boot/grub/custom.cfg:menuentry 'Windows' {
   search --fs-uuid --set=root $uuid
   chainloader /EFI/Microsoft/Boot/bootmgfw.efi
}Replace$uuidwith the actual filesystem UUID for the EFI system partition that contains bootmgfw.efi.Do we really need os-prober for a 2-line menuentry stanza? I think not...

